    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A CLASSIC JRPG FEEL</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/b652641bedaad4ca7f979cc8d4547e4f.poster.avif?t=1699660148\" width=620 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/b652641bedaad4ca7f979cc8d4547e4f.webm?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/b652641bedaad4ca7f979cc8d4547e4f.mp4?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Inspired by classic JRPGs like Final Fantasy and Dragon Quest, Spire will immerse you in its engaging story about a boy lost in a forgotten world. Placing his trust in a Spirit Guide this boy will partake on an epic journey to get back home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAUTIFULLY IMMERSIVE EXPERIENCE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/5c6018f7a6ba07699d9dde43a5a8ed43.poster.avif?t=1699660148\" width=620 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/5c6018f7a6ba07699d9dde43a5a8ed43.webm?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/5c6018f7a6ba07699d9dde43a5a8ed43.mp4?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you traverse the forgotten lands of this alternate world you’ll engage in a beautifully immersive experience that will leave you lost in this new universe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAST AND FLUID COMBAT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/08312ff8dc130ed855d20aee8f3f9dfd.poster.avif?t=1699660148\" width=620 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/08312ff8dc130ed855d20aee8f3f9dfd.webm?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/08312ff8dc130ed855d20aee8f3f9dfd.mp4?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enjoy fast, fluid and responsive combat as you fight your way through hordes of unique enemies and bosses!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE GAMEPLAY STYLE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/73d63238ab614c5f3211489573a6fc88.poster.avif?t=1699660148\" width=620 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/73d63238ab614c5f3211489573a6fc88.webm?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211040/extras/73d63238ab614c5f3211489573a6fc88.mp4?t=1699660148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your spirit guide will play three key roles in your journey throughout this game:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sword</li></ul> The spirit guide will transform from its fox form to its sword form which you can use in battle<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Healer</li></ul> When you find yourself low on health you can switch your spirit guide back to its fox form which will replenish your health over time<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Compass</li></ul> During your journey the fox will guide you in an effort to help you get back home",
